data.description: As the former model home for McIntosh Estates, this gorgeous 3,000+ sq ft Colonial includes all the best features! A soaring two-story foyer, gleaming hardwood floors, a beautiful eat-in kitchen, gas cooktop, built-in bookshelves, and a huge primary ensuite w/sitting room are just a glimpse of all to be discovered in this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home. You'll delight in the details of the built-in wine rack, the upscale finishes in the kitchen, the brick & stone hearth in the family room, and the custom cabinetry in the primary bath. Formal living and dining rooms, a home office/study, open concept kitchen/family room, and a big 4th bedroom/bonus room above the garage allow great spaces for gathering or privacy. Enjoy outdoor living on the newly topped deck or down in the yard on an expansive paver patio. Surrounded by trees, this 2.47-acre corner lot has lots room to play! The unfinished walk-out basement has a full bath rough-in and tons of potential for anything you need! A side-load 2-car garage, convenient mud room, and shed are extras that make this Hollywood beauty one that shouldn't be missed! Request your showing today!
